  "text": "With respect to treatment, [CITATION_1] reported that HA use was unsuccessful, but our data suggest otherwise. All 4 patients in our cohort with SII less than 0.75 use bilateral amplification devices. W03, W04, and W12 wear HAs and 1 W05 has CIs. Although hearing benefit was not formally assessed, the routine use of the devices by these patients is a subjective indicator of benefit.",
